      <title>阿波罗公司提拔两名高管，罗文将继续留任</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-15/apollo-promotes-two-senior-executives-rowan-is-staying-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Apollo Global Management Inc. 将 Jim Zelter 晋升为总裁，这是一个新职位。信贷主管 John Zito 将接替他担任资产管理业务联席总裁。与此同时，首席执行官 Marc Rowan 将签署一份为期五年的续约合同。彭博社的 Sridhar Natarajan 报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-15/apollo-promotes-two-senior-executives-rowan-is-staying-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 16:24:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Hegseth 谈确认之路：Invesco 的 Flitton</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-15/hegseth-on-path-to-confirmation-invesco-s-flitton-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Invesco 美国政府事务主管 Jennifer Flitton 表示，Pete Hegseth 很可能获得确认。她还认为，提名人阵容更强大，能够传达特朗普第二届政府的信息。她在“彭博监视”节目中与彭博社的 Jonathan Ferro、Annmarie Hordern 和 Dani Burger 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-15/hegseth-on-path-to-confirmation-invesco-s-flitton-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 15:48:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
