      <title>可可价格下跌，因交易商等待研磨数据寻找需求线索</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/cocoa-falls-as-traders-await-grindings-data-for-demand-clues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[可可期货下跌，因为市场正在等待主要消费地区的第四季度研磨数据，以寻找在价格创历史新高的情况下需求的线索。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/cocoa-falls-as-traders-await-grindings-data-for-demand-clues</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 13:20:41 GMT</pubDate>
